{"type": "article", "id": 13654, "title": "「 夏末单车」之车把小花瓶", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-18T08:03:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 13, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606140509aXynzVcrZItiSqTU.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t夏日里在自行车上带点儿花花草草，简直是凹小清新利器。如果载不了大花束或是花篮，插两枝小花小草也不错。这是一个 3D 打印做成的花瓶，刷上了清漆保证可以见水以及保持颜色的稳定，大小基本适合所有的自行车，可以被固定在车把上。同时，它的底部是平的，当没有出行时，也可以拿下来放在桌子上。<a href=\"http://www.wearableplanter.com/shop/geometric-handlebar-vase\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以购买。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141350gRkEZD2LdqtYSG4W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141351dtQwAq0ozNlaIhxR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141351jNoFrzAWEkanvJPL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141352570nHYQTCNgeEkSr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141353L4hZwiWCme375sGS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141353AwLmsRMx7qytPO2N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}